XVIII.3 Truth table skeleton for contradiction
Contradiction is checked per gate per season endpoint per cell.
Inputs:
obs_result
human_result
lab_result
Rules:
1.
If any two classes disagree on Boolean resolution (PASS vs FAIL), set
contradiction_flag = true.
2. If any class returns INSUFFICIENT_DATA, treat as FAIL for transition unless
doctrine sets PAUSED.
3. If contradiction_flag true, no advancement transitions allowed, apply increased
constraint or halt continuity.
XVIII.4 State machine skeletons
A. Seasonal Gate state machine
State variables:
SeasonState current_season
SeasonEndpoint last_endpoint
data_sufficiency_flag
Transitions:
UNDECLARED to SUMMER when Observational gate declares SUMMER
endpoint under persistence rules and data sufficiency true.
UNDECLARED to WINTER when Observational gate declares WINTER endpoint
under persistence rules and data sufficiency true.
SUMMER to WINTER when WINTER endpoint declared.
WINTER to SUMMER when SUMMER endpoint declared.
Any to PAUSED if ambiguity or contradiction exists at seasonal gate.
B. Cell service machine
IN_SERVICE to OUT_OF_SERVICE upon AccessBond activation and
disturbance start.
OUT_OF_SERVICE to IN_SERVICE only after withdrawal, rehabilitation
complete, and requalification passes PoP under stress windows.
Any to PAUSED upon tri witness contradiction that blocks settlement.
C. PoP to BGU accumulation machine
For each cell, per qualification window:
Guard conditions to count a BGU:
service_state == IN_SERVICE
seasonal endpoint finalised
PoP gate PASS for all declared processes
no critical dependency failures
no contradiction_flag true
If guard holds for the full declared stress window, increment
bgu_counter_current_window.
If any guard fails, set continuity_state = BROKEN for the window, reset
bgu_counter_current_window, record failure.
D. BGU to BDR advancement machine
Guard:
consecutive_valid_bgu_count meets activation threshold
EVUs finalised
no contradictions in the activation run
EDA constraints satisfied
Transition:
advance BDR stage by one, tighten issuance by EDA, optionally reduce issuance
velocity.
E. PoR upgrade machine
Guard:
continuity_state == CONTINUOUS
protection_state == PROTECTED
directional improvement in energy capture and community dynamics
important dependency not failed
contradiction_flag false
Transition:
regeneration_state = REGENERATING and permit PoR upgrade records.
F. Rectification machine
Trigger events:
contradiction detected
breach of subsistence bounds into market leakage
dependency failure with declared gating effect
data tampering or invalid witness signature
sustained INSUFFICIENT_DATA where doctrine disallows pause
Actions:
set service_state = PAUSED or OUT_OF_SERVICE, depending on trigger
increase constraint, extend qualification window, require higher confidence tier
EVUs
prohibit advancement, never rewrite past finalised BDR records
G. Reincarnation machine
Trigger:
implementation termination, severe governance compromise, catastrophic
witness integrity loss
Actions:
write version termination record
instantiate new version inheriting all constraints plus failure induced obligations
prohibit any relaxation of doctrine
